<p style="color:maroon;font-size:110%">
It may take a while to load the interactive plot. If it does not load,
please reload the page.
</p>
<ul>
    <li style="font-size:80%">Click the magnifier icon and choose the area to enlarge the area.</li>
    <li style="font-size:80%">Click the cross icon and hold the button to move around the area.</li>
    <li style="font-size:80%">Click the cross icon and then use the roller to zoom in and out.</li>
    <li style="font-size:80%">Click the house icon to go back to the full view.</li>
    <li style="font-size:80%">After enlarging the area with the magnifier, 
        use the cross icon to see the values of each data point.</li>
</ul>

<p style="color:maroon;font-size:110%">
The reaction speed of the page will be significantly slower if there are large numbers of data.
If that is the case, you may want to reduce the time span or the resolution.
</p>
